                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَمَا أَظُنُّ﴾ مَا أَعْتَقِدُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿غَلِيظٍ﴾ شَدِيدٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "51": {
